---
title: Carb Smart Beef Koftas with Veggie Hash and Garlic Hummus
description: Inspired by the ever-tasty and oh-so filling mezze platter, this veggie hash hits all the right notes without the need for pitas! Spiced beef koftas adorn golden hash packed full of peppers, carrots and zucchini. Don't forget to top it all off with the garlic hummus!

Carb Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
